    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ラジオの収録お疲れ様\nこの後はこのまま……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job with the radio recording.\nAfter this‚ we’ll just… huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.4149434168
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "……うーーん……\n…………うーーーーん…………",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Umm…\n…Ummmmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0482766151,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "こんな光景、昨日も見た気がするな……\nどうした、雫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like I saw this scene yesterday too…\nWhat’s wrong‚ Shizuku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.895442144
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、えっと……浴衣の通販をしようと思って\n昨日から、見てるんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ um… I was thinking of buying a yukata online…\nI’ve been looking since yesterday‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.8954420089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.8621088106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ほしいと思ったのは、売り切れてたり\n配送が間に合わなかったりして……全滅",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ones I wanted are either sold out or\nwon’t be delivered in time…It’s hopeless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5205383002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.2287754773
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか……分かった、俺も探して……\nう……ダメだな、どれも届くまで二週間前後か……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Alright‚ I’ll help you look too…\nHmm… Nope‚ they all take about two weeks to arrive…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "もっと早めに頼めば良かったけど……\n仕方ない、よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I should have ordered sooner‚ but…\nIt can’t be helped.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.3873012859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.5873016753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのみんなとお祭りに行けるだけで\n絶対、楽しいし……十分",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just going to the festival with everyone from Sunny Peace\nwill be… fun enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8539682069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.5873016753
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "でも、一人だけ私服なのは\n寂しいって言ってたじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you said you’d feel lonely\nbeing the only one in casual clothes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.4709295112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "それは、そう、だけど……\n間に合わないのは、しょうがない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yes‚ but…\nIf it doesn’t arrive in time‚ there’s nothing I can do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4709295112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……分かった、なら今から直接お店に買いに行こう\n少しだけだが、次の仕事まで時間がある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright‚ then let’s go buy one from a store now.\nWe have a little time before the next job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.0000002543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.1553061085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、直接、お店に……！？\nそんな大胆なこと、私、出来る、かな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait‚ directly from a store…?\nCan I really do something so bold…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8553059735,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.1219712493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "お店の人に話し掛けられたら、どうしよう……\nき、緊張してきた……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if the shop staff talk to me…?\nI-I’m getting nervous…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4236915916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺もいるから大丈夫だよ\nとにかく行ってみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll be with you‚ so it’s okay.\nLet’s just go and see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.766665395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――アパレルショップに到着して三十分",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――30 minutes after arriving at the apparel shop…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2048282699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.2048281349
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.2048281349
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "雫、そろそろ決まったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ have you decided yet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.1381600774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "こっちは怜ちゃんのイメージに被るし……\nこの花柄は、さくらちゃんっぽい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This one overlaps with Rei-chan's image…\nThis floral pattern looks like Sakura-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.042305326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.2423039352
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "このデザインは遙子さんに似合いそう……！\nあ、この紫陽花柄は千紗ちゃんにぴったり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This design would suit Haruko-san…!\nOh‚ this hydrangea pattern is perfect for Chisa-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.5642245966,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "雫、雫……\n一体、誰の浴衣選びなんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ Shizuku…\nWhose yukata are you picking out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0666628519,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.8882221932
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん、推しのアイドル……！\nはっ……違う、今日は自分のを選ぶんだった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ for my favorite idols…!\nAh… no‚ today I’m supposed to pick mine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.088223584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 123.7548888599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "全部素敵で……目移りしちゃって……\nそしたら、みんなに似合いそうだなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They’re all so wonderful… I’m getting distracted…\nAnd then I start thinking they’d look good on everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.188223584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "私に似合うの……\n似合う……に～あ～う～……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What would suit me…\nSuit… suuuuuiiiit…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.0548902507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.9215555265
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\n私に似合うのって、どんな浴衣、かな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nWhat kind of yukata would suit me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.952795195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_apparelshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "apparelshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.5215555265
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "まずは、自分が着たいと思うものが一番だ\n俺の考えもあるが、先にいいと思ったのを教えてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "First‚ the most important thing is what you want to wear.\nI have my own thoughts‚ but tell me what you like first.",
